verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Name that to our hearts is nearest,
Here the stricken soul doth hide;
Name that to our hearts is dearest,
As in Jesus we confide.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}“Call Him Jesus!” He shall save us
From the tyranny of sin;
From its condemnation save us,
From iniquity within.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Jesus! sweetest note of any
In the lowly pilgrim’s song;
Jesus! the triumphant music
Of the bright angelic throng.{/lang-eng}
